{"tid":1729732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兄弟 爬山，各自努力 已被忘？","createTime":"2019-11-17T10:36:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T10:52:50.000Z","uid":146749,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"09aded69b5aa2f1887922a63cef7d266d00cdb07","tid":1729732,"uid":146749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:36:22.000Z","msg":"中大理大被包圍<br />\n當中最好就係其他地區分散注意力就係<span style=\"color: red;\">18區開花</span><br />\n但部份地區人數往往未必達到安全快閃人數令在場手足做唔到野<br />\n<br />\n有無人想過和理非呢？去左邊？<br />\n大家要認清現實和理非好難走會上前<br />\n<br />\n咁點解唔試下再次和勇齊上，和理非在主要交通公路旁例如黃大仙廣場舉行個和理唱等等的活動，而勇武就去快閃，同時cover勇武又可以吸引popo注意，最重要係和理非有野做同時又可以話比所有前線知有人支持緊大家<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n兄弟 爬山，各自努力<br />\n光復香港，時代革命"},{"pid":"6de516f4c71c656dce2e43adc449229d26e51f3f","tid":1729732,"uid":146749,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:37:23.000Z","msg":"推，我想和理非都幫下手"},{"pid":"917bc5c713159b312e4a9a9c4e74ec9de5cf7534","tid":1729732,"uid":146749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:37:54.000Z","msg":"推，我想和理非都幫下手"},{"pid":"2008afbdec1a4440df2a2c5766876c3f72456a75","tid":1729732,"uid":35125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:38:02.000Z","msg":"幫手呀"},{"pid":"8d4acc77c4ba02b228fd54331d148a407c210ce6","tid":1729732,"uid":338630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:38:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99edc08fae21ca740564e68b7bd3b3cf9a8b09d0","tid":1729732,"uid":338630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-17T10:38:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im